				<h2>Why does microstepping give less torque?</h2>
<p>I am experimenting with using a stepper motor for a robotics project. I'd like to use microstepping to give a better resolution and smoother movement, but I have noticed that the finer the microsteps, the lower the torque from the motor. Why is this?</p>

